{
  "texts": [
    "Besides, suitable datasets and evaluation criteria are worth pursuing.",
    "Currently, most Chinese sign language datasets are too small and non-standard.",
    "Meanwhile, the proportion of experiments is high, and the promotion of applications is insufficient.",
    "All of these aspects need improvement.",
    "Furthermore, based on the integration of multiple modalities and the intersection of multi-perspective technologies, there is an urgent need to develop systems with efficient and accurate recognition.As a whole, the Chinese Sign Language Recognition model has achieved favorable overall evaluation indicators."
  ]
}